"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[Cryptocurrency](https://www.binance.com/en/register?ref=CVPPUTEK) custody firm New York Digital Investment Group (NYDIG) announced an equity funding round that saw a massive $1 billion in growth capital.\\n\\n* The company announced the news of the funding round in a [press release](https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/nydig-announces-1-billion-funding-round-301444063.html) on Tuesday (Dec. 14, 2021). Consequently, the new capital brings NYDIG’s valuation to $7 billion.\\n* According to the statement, the round was led by growth equity firm WestCap, with existing investors and partners such as Bessemer Venture Partners, FinTech Collective, Morgan Stanley, New York Life, MassMutual, Affirm, Fiserv, and FIS also participating in the billion-dollar round.\\n* Commenting on the latest development was NYDIG’s co-founder and CEO, Robert Gutmann, who said:\\n\\n> “Our roster of partnerships and strategic investors lays the foundation for NYDIG to become the leading provider of [Bitcoin](https://www.binance.com/en/register?ref=CVPPUTEK) solutions for businesses in any industry, and this new equity capital will further accelerate progress towards making this exciting network accessible – and useful – to all.”\\n\\n* The [crypto](https://www.binance.com/en/register?ref=CVPPUTEK) custody firm said it will use the raised funds to further upgrade its institutional-grade [bitcoin](https://www.binance.com/en/register?ref=CVPPUTEK) platform, enable support for asset tokenization, [bitcoin](https://www.binance.com/en/register?ref=CVPPUTEK) and Lightning payments, and smart contracts.\\n* Furthermore, the capital should help the company to increase its workforce globally.\\n* Meanwhile, the funding round comes shortly after NYDIG [partnered](https://cryptopotato.com/financial-giant-ncr-teams-up-with-nydig-to-let-650-u-s-banks-offer-bitcoin-services/) with payments giant National Cash Register (NCR) to enable 650 American banks to offer [bitcoin](https://www.binance.com/en/register?ref=CVPPUTEK) services.\\n* Another partnership was recently inked with MassMutual, which sought to [allow bitcoin access](https://cryptopotato.com/massmutual-doubles-down-by-partnering-with-nydig-to-grant-institutions-access-to-bitcoin/) to select customers.\\n\\n```\\nSPECIAL OFFER (Sponsored)\\nBinance Free $100 (Exclusive): Use this link to register and receive $100 free and 10% off fees on Binance Futures first month (terms).PrimeXBT Special Offer: Use this link to register & enter POTATO50 code to get 50% free bonus on any deposit up to $1750.\\n```\",\"timestamp\":1639504181,\"title\":\"WestCap Leads a $1 Billion Funding Round for NYDIG, Values the Company at $7B\"},\"digest\":\"Q3n_0lZTTawJ1xVWVrZu6FT6JFKZ3nGDsNXvolJiQLc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xb10302Deb61EEdCc01d017659CfACeB54FB4a661\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aCsPAFVcqif0il3tGb-KL78lfzMLPzjcWYYnOSKhbxo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7weVJmd2OkyOeLydM1gMNvbJpc0GjvJiAbm_GPVaG2g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"wMAJHi6pwL2e__svFCNrDYt7K1926z2Ig4aAdSLcBVy1ca9lyeQYT9i-rbiCFcTq-APzqtZRicKo8SnOUt7tLA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc40a401542280d3d56ba85ce83938f4d17d7644a7746bca69d7b10c01afcf05c38cd68aca8f3276c7efb13695759f3127b5b96507140ac90366ec021ee64e7461b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"aCsPAFVcqif0il3tGb-KL78lfzMLPzjcWYYnOSKhbxo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7weVJmd2OkyOeLydM1gMNvbJpc0GjvJiAbm_GPVaG2g\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Q3n_0lZTTawJ1xVWVrZu6FT6JFKZ3nGDsNXvolJiQLc\"}"